content:
Add the Admission Application Items FlexCard to the individual application record page layout to show the application items that require verification or that were rejected by a reviewer. Admissions personnel can see all education, examination, and file records that are in the unverified or rejected status.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise, Unlimited, and Developer editions where the Education Cloud license is enabled.

Who: Users with the Education Cloud Full Access, Education Cloud Limited Access, or Education Cloud Reviewer permission set can use this feature.
title: Quick View of Admissions Item Status in Salesforce
